  <brief_title>Assessment of Pain and Quality of Life in Breast and Prostate Cancer Patients With Bone Metastases</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Open-label Study to Determine the Effect of iv. Zoledronic Acid on Pain and Quality of Life in Patients With Bone Metastases With or Without Skeletal Related Events (SRE) Resulting From Breast Cancer and Prostate Cancer</official_title>
