  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety, tolerability and efficacy of zoledronic acid
      administered intravenously every 3-4 weeks in patients with bone metastases from either
      breast cancer or prostate cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
